{"tid":2498171,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[NS] Monster Hunter Rise (49) 4月末配信予定 Ver.2.0","createTime":"2021-04-21T03:52:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T04:46:04.000Z","uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b23355864b6cd33dd0f4ad5c7f93d781204468df","tid":2498171,"uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"> <img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EiH0xW3VkAYbnxc?format=jpg&amp;name=large\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEiH0xW3VkAYbnxc%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dlarge&h=ffa537e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</p><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><a href=\"https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmhrise.wiki-db.com%2Fsim%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=214f5724\" target=\"_blank\">https://mhrise.wiki-db.com/sim/</a><br />\n<strong>MHR混裝器</strong></p><br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n4月尾2.0更新<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmf2L41eHSTazbXsLfoKUyQPZjKswkFMztSwuuH6Aorfq3?filename=Rsn1uM1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRsn1uM1.jpg&h=cab87907&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3月26日(五)發售<br />\nAlso available on PC(Steam 2022)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官方網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monsterhunter.com%2Frise%2Fhk%2F&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=abbf3dd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.monsterhunter.com/rise/hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">Q&amp;A </span></span><br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔同版本有咩分別？可唔可以連機？<br />\nA: 日版 港版有中文 美版冇中文<br />\nSwitch MHR冇分ser 全版本可以連機 (需要Nintendo Switch Online)<br />\n<br />\nQ: 新手用咩武器好？<br />\nA: 14種武器各有長短 試下打村任熟習下<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點拎特典？<br />\nA: 火芽左邊隻貓郵差&gt;新增內容<br />\n<br />\nQ : 點係地圖閃燈俾隊友睇<br />\nA : 係場地入邊禁住-號放大地圖，再禁-號<br />\n<br />\nQ : 殺完大怪之後動畫點Skip ?<br />\nA : 兩下B制<br />\n<br />\nQ : 隨從廣場點先開放?<br />\nA : 要行一次先會開到，係火芽面向個位直行到橋尾<br />\n<br />\nQ : 神火卷點拎？<br />\nA : 村5星後玩村任 村長有機會派<br />\n<br />\nQ : 海境S點出？<br />\nA : 玩交易船<br />\n<br />\nQ : 打完boss好似未完咁？<br />\nA : 要等更新！<br />\n<br />\nQ : 貓其實有咩技最好<br />\nA : 兩個技必要<br />\n- 強化咆哮 +30%會心<br />\n- cooldown時間一分鐘, 成鋪大部份時間都會發動緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 強化太鼓 x1.05倍攻, x1.2倍防<br />\n- cooldown時間90秒<br />\n<br />\nTips:<br />\n1. 有咩睇咗獵人筆記/心得先<br />\n<br />\n2. 連機嫌眼花可以熄特效<br />\n<br />\n3. 隨從廣場有棵樹可以爬上去 每次完任都有嘢可以執<br />\n（**可以儲一陣先執 唔洗每次去攞）<br />\n<br />\n4. 撳實L1左下角個小地圖可以睇到詳細地圖標記咗嘅嘢 搵礦有小小用<br />\n<br />\n5. 礦有唔少都喺啲勁高嘅地方 要用翔蟲飛嚟飛去 可以配合L1地圖去搵<br />\n<br />\n6. 船艇牡蠣 : 寒冷群島搵 / 狐火鬼燈 : 大社遺跡搵<br />\n<br />\n7. 村任2★ 上 3★要去一去隨從廣場(村右邊過橋)同寵物店老闆吹水<br />\n<br />\n8.村任打完5星 會有個特別許可任務<br />\n連續狩獵打完火龍雷狼同泥翁就可以直接打集會個hr4既首領青熊獸百龍夜行，打完直上hr4<br />\n<br />\n9. 集會所任務出發前記得食團子(即係上幾代既貓飯)<br />\n<br />\n10 : 入左場地之後，-號可以進入地圖，,再L及R睇到好多資訊<br />\n<br />\n11: 下位唔駛諗砌裝，堆高個防就夠<br />\n<br />\n12: ZL+ZR可以直接向瞄準既地方飛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n開潛艇（新農場）教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D5786%26snA%3D159411&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=2a40cee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=5786&amp;snA=159411</a><br />\n<br />\n測試有冇中痛風 :<br />\n<a href=\"https://gamewith.jp/mhrize/article/show/270133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgamewith.jp%2Fmhrize%2Farticle%2Fshow%2F270133&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=24addb40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gamewith.jp/mhrize/article/show/270133</a><br />\n<br />\n痛風表護石List :<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14/edit\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14%2Fedit&d=Hmcjt6vcQR8GyvD5m8y4dB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=2e733a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1wMYUsbmh1T4apAGNG0FANH_kC6JMslqFNM7I300mm14/edit</a><br />\n<br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"46169531b65c146196ab92fbf4d3d6666cb17b38","tid":2498171,"uid":4399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e40484e884fb3799d8a794c051fc35dddb30a5","tid":2498171,"uid":30698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"誤中1001<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66a5fb1e9a16f4f18eb3d08acc67e705366b2178","tid":2498171,"uid":37020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"94f3dcc68596812c8c1f910a07272e77c13e4cbf","tid":2498171,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:56:13.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"98cc19f2191f493cbb5cc1984710a45067bb806e","tid":2498171,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"新手幾日無追post<br />\n痛風即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f1653e40e1ad1fb6732bbcea33472b4dbc58f7","tid":2498171,"uid":1761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:58:20.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">連登輕弩雷神團基本教學: </span><br />\n懶人包:<br />\n裝用迅弩帶貫強超心+會心技(上位替換：攻7貫3速2弱2 <span class=\"red\">需要速1護石</span>, 上上位替換：攻7貫3速3 <span class=\"red\">需要速2護石</span>)<br />\n背包帶鬼人相關藥同貫2調合<br />\n只用貫2射有雷電部位<br />\n見擊龍孖寶解鎖就馬上用<br />\n見炮台就上去射<br />\n做唔到返去野團慢慢練<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621f97e39ea97214d815b31087e656f967352876","tid":2498171,"uid":370860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:59:02.000Z","msg":"xdptsa<br />\n貓重雷神團"},{"pid":"a997ed9236f205c99fc44a2f889ceb3a7070d771","tid":2498171,"uid":1761,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98cc19f2191f493cbb5cc1984710a45067bb806e","tid":2498171,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:57:53.000Z","msg":"新手幾日無追post<br />\n痛風即係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T03:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmefUZEDgZZo1Tspt1cqBLuRQ4bC97WvQAqqa9vCj6vg7j?filename=ezOrYgc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FezOrYgc.png&h=67286224&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e50d37c8fe1662d0fa90c1eb9f3234726308d627","tid":2498171,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"咁 特殊收刀 成日會變左 翻滾 <br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444dbc63312e15282ed66672048317e74573ab06","tid":2498171,"uid":37020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e50d37c8fe1662d0fa90c1eb9f3234726308d627","tid":2498171,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:02:07.000Z","msg":"咁 特殊收刀 成日會變左 翻滾 <br />\n點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:02:51.000Z","msg":"唔係咩動作都接到落特殊收刀"},{"pid":"4a096215e4d7e7eec2469c2e2ecfc82d138e1bf0","tid":2498171,"uid":95609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"58c4477ce94229dafc294a51c65032c0f7a3e226","tid"